# Self-Documentation

When you establish a new convention, resolve an ambiguity, or make a pattern decision that should persist across sessions, mention it to the user and suggest documenting it. If approved, use the `document-learnings` skill to route the update to the correct rule or skill file.

Do not self-document trivial or one-off decisions.
